docker run -d \
  --name c-neo4j \
  --network n-raogaru \
  -p 7474:7474 \
  -p 7687:7687 \
  -v v-neo4j-data:/data \
  -v v-neo4j-logs:/logs \
  i-neo4j


http://localhost:7474


Connect from Another Container (Same Network)
bolt://c-neo4j:7687


connect from java app
spring.neo4j.uri=bolt://c-neo4j:7687
spring.neo4j.authentication.username=neo4j
spring.neo4j.authentication.password=StrongPassword123

What Should Be Persisted (Critical)
/data      → graph store
/logs      → diagnostics
/import    → CSV imports
/plugins   → APOC & extensions

